steps.name: I skip linking my card
I handle"Stay Informed About Offers Pane" marketing consent
I accept "Stay Informed About Offers Pane" marketing consent
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I mock the location of the device to "DENMARK_10888"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Profile" tab is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "DENMARK_10888" station
I check "Set Location" page is visible
I enter the site ID "DENMARK_10888" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I handle"Stay Informed About Offers Pane" marketing consent
I accept "Stay Informed About Offers Pane" marketing consent
I click on "STORES" button
I check that the "Stores Screen" is displayed
I click on "VIEW LIST/MAP" button
I click on "SEARCH BAR" input
I enter the "Denmark" in the "SEARCH BAR" input
I check that the "Search Results Screen" is displayed
I click on "Denmark" search result
I check that the "Station List Screen" is displayed
I verify the store card list
I verify the store name on Store card
I check that the application text: "CIRCLE K #10742" isn't empty
I verify the store address on store card
I check that the application text: "2100 København Ø" isn't empty
I verify the store city on store card
I check that the application text: "2100 København Ø" isn't empty
I verify the store distance on Store card
I check that the application text: "7.2 km" isn't empty
I verify the store open status on store card
I check that the application text: "Open" isn't empty
I verify the store open hours on store card
I check that the application text: "- 24 hours" isn't empty
I verify that the store card is displayed with "Store details" button
I check that the application text: "STORE DETAILS" is equals to expected value: "STORE DETAILS"
I verify the Get Directions CTA
I check that the application text: "GET DIRECTIONS" is equals to expected value: "GET DIRECTIONS"
